Here are a few things I wish all girls knew... 

Instyle and I Am That Girl are raising the standards for how girls see themselves, and each other, and I'm so proud to be a part of this. 

These are some of the things I feel deeply and strongly about.. And I wish I could convey that to all the girls out there.. 

Yes, I believe in a woman having curves. 
Yes, I love my burgers.
Yes, I don't like being weak.
I am me, and I don't apologize for it. 
And you shouldn't either.
